creator: DH3 Games
descriptionHtml:
Test your love with this Love Tester app!

Looking to find out if you are in love with someone? If you are, this love test calculator app is exactly what you are looking for.

Answer ten questions and our unique algorithm with calculate the love compatibility as a percentage.There's a total of 5 different love test quizzes to try out!

Do you really love him/her? Does he like me? Does she like me? Is it true love or just friendship? Is it the perfect match? Find it out with our Love Test today and share the love calculator results with friends or friends. This is a great game for couples.

The Love Calculator enables you calculate the probability of a successful relationship between two people. No fingerprint or kissing is needed.

Love Calculator is great game to play with your BFF friends or family. You can take it it turns completing a love quiz.

Love Questions:

❤️ Am I in love?
❤️ Is it real love?
❤️ Is he my type?
❤️ Is she my type?
❤️ Does he like me?
❤️ Does she like me?
❤️ Have I found my soulmate?
❤️ Is he my true love?
❤️ Is she my true love?
❤️ Do I love my boyfriend?
❤️ Do I love my girlfriend?
❤️ Does my crush like me?
❤️ Is it love or friendship?
❤️ Is this relationship compatible?
❤️ Do you have a future with your partner?

Please note this app/game has been developed only for entertainment purposes and has no intention to hurt the user feelings. The application uses numerical algorithm to calculate the love match and should be used only for fun.

What are you waiting for? Give our Love Test Calculator a try! Install the Love Tester 2020 today and start using our calculator to check who your best love match is. Find your compatibility rating today!
